<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="drill-n">drill <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /drɪl/    美 /drɪl/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1c">1.<strong>[C] 钻；钻头；钻机：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an electric drill
电钻</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(反复的) 练习；操练：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The teacher gave the class plenty of drills in arithmetic.
老师让学生们做大量的算术练习。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a ﬁre drill
消防演习</p></div></div>